>> NOORY: Thank you so much.

00:28:05.966 --> 00:28:07.250 align:middle line:10%
Time travel.

00:28:07.250 --> 00:28:11.050 align:middle line:10%
It's not possible today, but
it could be possible tomorrow.

00:28:11.050 --> 00:28:13.980 align:middle line:10%
And if it does,
where would you go?

00:28:13.980 --> 00:28:17.490 align:middle line:10%
Would you go into the
